        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_sub_title",
        "text": "Verse 10.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " - This verse should read on continuously with the preceding, as far as to the word \"enemies.\" The time here denoted will stretch from the people's occupation of the laud to the death of Saul, as the expression, \"at the beginning,\" in ver. 9, will point to the experience of Egyptian oppression. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "Will build thee an house",
        "children": []
      },
